    "data": [
        {
            "title": "Meta推出Muse Spark AI模型獲分析師正面評價",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GQcDb8ntU.u8og0ujZxDlw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEAB20CL_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 週三,<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Meta\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Meta;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Meta\">Meta</a> Platforms推出Muse Spark,這是其新成立的Meta超級智能實驗室的首個模型,華爾街分析師對此反應積極,認為此次發布消除了該股的一個關鍵不確定性因素。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Muse Spark是一個原生多模態推理模型,支持工具使用、視覺思維鏈和多代理編排。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該模型現已在Meta AI和meta.ai上推出,預計未來幾週將在WhatsApp、Instagram、Facebook、Messenger和Meta智能眼鏡上進行更廣泛的部署。私有API預覽版已向部分用戶開放。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-017220ca-895f-320e-bcff-12fa3376c73b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利分析師Brian Nowak給予Meta增持評級和775美元目標價,他稱Muse Spark是\"重新評估META的第一步\",並指出基準測試表現好於投資者的擔憂。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Nowak寫道:\"基準測試的重要性不及META將其自有模型能力產品化的能力\",他強調早期階段的購物助手是一個重要的代理商務機會。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國銀行分析師Justin Post重申對Meta的買入評級和885美元目標價,並指出此次發布早於媒體報導暗示可能推遲至5月的時間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Post將其與谷歌Gemini的發展軌跡進行比較,認為如果模型性能持續改善,Meta\"在未來12個月可能會走上類似的軌跡\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"在約625美元的價位,Meta按華爾街預測的2027年GAAP每股收益計算估值為18倍(調整強化學習投資後為15倍),低於標普500指數的約20倍。考慮到巨大的AI機遇、高於行業的廣告增長以及AI領域的強大財務實力,我們認為當前估值具有吸引力。重申買入評級,\"Post寫道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師還指出,Muse Spark有潛力增強廣告定向、提高廣告支出回報率,並最終支持訂閱收入流。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/meta%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BAmuse-spark-ai%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%B8%AB%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%A2%E8%A9%95%E5%83%B9-113234260.html",
